<bibRefCitation author="Takeda M &amp; Kurata Y" box="[1074,1369,1185,1209]" pageId="53" pageNumber="498" pagination="91 - 111" refId="ref77695" refString="Takeda M, Kurata Y. 1977. Crabs of the Ogasawara Islands IV. A collection made at the new volcanic island, Nishinoshima-shinto, in 1975. Bulletin of the National Science Museum, Tokyo, series A, Zoology 3 (2): 91 - 111, figs 1 - 9." type="journal article" year="1977">TAKEDA &amp; KURATA, 1977</bibRefCitation>
